title: Ep 367 - Tappu Sleeps Early
shortDesc: Jethalal comes home to give him the new game he had requested. But when he goes to Tappu's room to give it to him, he will see Tappu already deep in sleep. Surprised, Jethalal wonders if Tappu has become a good boy.

title: Ep 368  - Kids And Modern Technology
shortDesc: Parents are sick of watching kids play games in their rooms all day long. They try to send the kids out to play, but they all ens up at Dr. Hathi's place. How will the parents find a solution to this new age addiction?

title: Ep 369 - Champaklals Fool Proof Idea
shortDesc: Champaklal advises the parents to start playing in the society and that would distract the kids and would bring them down to the society. Will this plan work? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 370 - A Scary Parcel For Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: While the society members are playing in the compound, a tempo arrives to deliver a parcel. When they see it, all the members scream and run away. What is inside the truck? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep  371 - The Simple Game Of A Scarf
shortDesc: Champaklal organizes a simple game using just a scarf. He divides the society members into two and makes them play this game. Whose team will win? Gogi's or Tappu's team?

title: Ep 372 - Anjalis Surprising Delivery
shortDesc: Anjali orders for a few delicious food ingredients which shocksTaarak. Learning that Anjali is cooking all of that yummy food, Taarak gets excited and promises to take her to the movies. Meanwhile, Bhide is having a bad day. Watch to find out how.

title: Ep 373 - Tappu And Sonus Results Are With The Principal
shortDesc: It is the result day at school and the entire Tappu Sena is at the school to collect the results. But at the school, the teacher says that Tappu and Sonu should collect their results from the principal. How will the meeting go?

title: Ep  374 - Komals Complaint Against Goli
shortDesc: Its vacation time for the kids and Komal is worried about Goli. She brings him to Taarak so that he can get some knowledge about life and the importance of education. How will Taarak help?

title: Ep 375 - Black Money
shortDesc: One of Jethalal's friends hands him 50 lakh rupees in cash in a steel box. Later, Daya gives Madhavi lentils to prepare papad in the same steel box. Is there going to be a confusion?

title: Ep 376 - Taarak Talks About Black Money
shortDesc: Taarak takes a day off from work to write an article on corruption. He asks Anjali what would happen if all the black money from the Swiss accounts come back to our country. Watch the entire episode to know what happens next.

title: Ep 377 - Taarak Needs A Lift
shortDesc: Taarak with the box full of cash asks Sodhi for a lift til Jethalal's shop. Due to some problem in his jeep, he asks Taarak to push the jeep for it to start.

title: Ep 378 - Where Is The Money?
shortDesc: When Taarak reaches Gada Electronics, Jethalal and his friend eagerly await to open the box with the money. As soon as they open the box, they find lentils instead of the cash. Where did the money go?

title: Ep 379 - Bhide Is The New Suspect
shortDesc: Daya, Jethalal and his friend go to Bhide's house to get the box only to find out that Bhide has given all the boxes to Sodhi for grinding the lentils. When Madhavi and Bhide come to know that the box had so much cash, they are numb.

title: Ep 380 - Bharat Threatens Jethalal
shortDesc: After Abdul is found missing, Bharat suspects Abdul to have stolen the money. He later threatens Jethalal to file a police complaint against him. Will Jethalal land into a legal trouble?

title: Ep 381 - Tappu Sena Wastes Water
shortDesc: After playing for a while in the garden, everyone in the Tappu Sena is dirty and full of mud. When Bhide comes into the compound, he sees Tappu Sena play with water and shower with it.
